snippet.title: Dune: Awakening | Exclusive Gameplay Reveal | Into The Infinite 2024
snippet.description:
Step into the vast, unforgiving world of Arrakis in Dune: Awakening, an Open World Survival MMO. Survive and thrive in a seamless, shared world where thousands of players interact, forming alliances and rivalries. Gather resources, build your stronghold, and navigate political intrigue to dominate the desert planet. Developed by Funcom.

Add to your Steam wishlist: https://lvli.li/DUNEASTEAM
